		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform2" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=600"><span id=Guru>PraetorFenix</span></a><b><span id=Guru><br>Guru</span></b><br><img src=/shared/user_star_ico.gif height=9 width=9><img src=/shared/user_star_ico.gif height=9 width=9><br>279 posts
		   <br><nobr><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [5.00]</nobr><br><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=PraetorFenix&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform2" width="100%"><p><i>(Edit:&nbsp;&nbsp;All my calculation formulae can be found <a href=HTTP://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/classes.html?class=6&mid=9666207458401 target=akztarg>here</a>.  I keep forgetting that not everybody knows about that stuff..)</i><br><br><i>(Edit 2:  Methmetician?  Like a druggie?  I wish we could edit titles too.)</i><br><br>First of all, let's completely disregard the procs on these weapons.  Since nobody really knows how they work completely, let's pretend they don't exist.<br><br>Also, I am assuming a strength of 150, and that every swing will land a successful hit.<br><br>Dual wield percent for a level 60 warrior is approximately 75%.<br>_______________________________________________________________________<br><br>Let's take the <a href=HTTP://eqdb.allakhazam.com/item.html?item=2631 target=akztarg>Jagged Blade of War</a> and it's little cousins, the <a href=HTTP://eqdb.allakhazam.com/item.html?item=2630 target=akztarg>Blade of Strategy</a> and the <a href=HTTP://eqdb.allakhazam.com/item.html?item=2629 target=akztarg>Blade of Tactics</a>.  For those who don't know, these are the result of <a href=HTTP://eqdb.allakhazam.com/quest.html?quest=768 target=akztarg>the warrior epic quest</a>.<br><br>With the Jagged Blade of War in both hands:<br><br>Your minimum damage will be 21.<br>Your maximum damage will be ~167-169<br>Your magic number will be 92<br>You will get ~14.63 swings per minute<br><b>Therefore you will do 1592 damage per minute with the Jagged Blade of War.</b><br><br>With the Blade of Strategy in your primary hand:<br><br>Your minimum damage will be 12.<br>Your maximum damage will be ~68-70.<br>Your magic number will be 39.<br>You will get exactly 25 swings per minute.<br>Therefore you will do 1199 damage per minute with the Blade of Strategy in the primary hand.<br><br>But remember, you have the Blade of Tactics on the offhand:<br><br>Your minimum damage will be 1.<br>Your maximum damage will be ~57-59.<br>Your magic number will be 28.<br>You will get ~18.75 swings per minute<br>Therefore you will do 567 damage per minute with the Blade of Strategy in the offhand.<br><br><b>And you will do 1766 damage per minute wielding both the Blade of Strategy and the Blade of Tactics.</b><br><br>And now we have a pretty little picture <a href=HTTP://www.geocities.com/canadiantemplar/uberwarrior.jpg target=akztarg>right here</a>.<br><br>As previous posters mentioned, damage for dual wield becomes greater around level 35.  Although, it is nice to have both maxed.  I hope this helps a bit!</p><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br><b>Praetor</b>, 65th Lord Protector of Ascent (Retired)<br><b>Tiresias</b>, 1st Warrior of Asura (Hopefully)</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0 width="100%"><tr><td id=fs8></td><td align=right id=fs8 >2 Replies</td></tr></table><table width="100%"><tr><td class=mhback>&nbsp;</td><td class=mhback >Thread Subject</a></td><td class=mhback>Started by</a></td><td class=mhback>Replies</a></td><td class=mhback>Last Post</a></td><td class=mhback>Rating</a></td></tr><tr class=mdr>
